{"tid":1683091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人既憤怒係咪剩係keep到去最近既紅日/weekend","createTime":"2019-10-30T12:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T02:14:25.000Z","uid":14699,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f2e27246d08dc89b40f5525d70f96f78248c235f","tid":1683091,"uid":14699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:58:39.000Z","msg":"呢場係一場長期抗爭，每一次既集會遊行都需要人。反抗唔係打完卡 po ig 就反抗左，係需要人行出黎去展露我地既決心，每個人行出一少步就等於一大步。<br />\n<br />\n721 831 徹夜未眠<br />\n101 中槍無比憤怒<br />\n呢d日子真香港人係冇可能忘記，情緒有起伏什至抑鬱。當大家睇直播睇到好擔心好心痛，為何不<span style=\"color: red;\">化悲憤為力量，情感轉為化行動</span>，與港人同行光復香港。<br />\n<br />\n驚，每個出黎既人都驚，面對極權驚乃人之常情。每次出門口都會諗返唔返到屋企洗唔洗寫定遺書，但一次又一次見到手足堅持一齊走上街頭，心靈上都會得到安慰。因為我知仲有同路人一同奮鬥，我地係一家人，我地共同分擔，我地互相支撐，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地要驚既一齊驚</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n路係人行出黎，二千幾位手足擋子彈負上法律責任開闢出黎既路讓大家跟上，一同前進，就係差你一個。可否答應我唔好辜負手足既負出？<br />\n<br />\n我願將來呢幅畫入面既唔單只有義士，而係所有走上街頭既真香港人，一同為正義時代革命，一同創造屬於我地既歷史，屬於我地既香港。<br />\n<br />\n112要係維園見到大家<br />\n黎緊既路都要係街頭見到大家<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wzYFkkT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwzYFkkT.png&h=9e581112&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7kDwBC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7kDwBC.jpg&h=6da1c92c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"622ef2a95d9a414f31113328df53fc41ed19416d","tid":1683091,"uid":14699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:00:21.000Z","msg":"香港人同我出黎"},{"pid":"8ef55ad563d22fd0b323ab40d063f7a1a72f7cdb","tid":1683091,"uid":14699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:03:16.000Z","msg":"112 維園見"},{"pid":"f90b1f8478656ae8deaefd01fd311d5223d5e7a6","tid":1683091,"uid":38931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ecec04c0f48dd9a23d05caabb9939a7df87c81","tid":1683091,"uid":14699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:07:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/10_Fipf0_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F10_Fipf0_1200x0.jpg&h=3f7024a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e39fcd43ef40b362c7dbfb09cdd33bb27ace5edf","tid":1683091,"uid":115416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:08:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89daeab8d83af92b8ffc33410885e2adb95cab1c","tid":1683091,"uid":14699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:11:06.000Z","msg":"多一個真係好多"},{"pid":"17dfb25bfd460597b20fe9bbc49d59c23bb75e6b","tid":1683091,"uid":14699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:14:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf25668307d20323adda05e7011879e0e96844a3","tid":1683091,"uid":261239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:15:54.000Z","msg":"香港人 112 見！不見不散！"},{"pid":"d6157f757527aab1d68252d9c900f7240916c32f","tid":1683091,"uid":14699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:20:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afce99a40d71ad77bf5b165e454e6651cce81b2b","tid":1683091,"uid":14699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:27:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d9ad9cdf730c87fdd30fc8ac9e9daba5db6ecd","tid":1683091,"uid":184433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:28:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7241ca56b1b1924c4c7fd840f477c1ee1598e5b2","tid":1683091,"uid":14699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T13:39:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d147c2b4b1acf10fa896f63f33a1e393c3c87f91"